name: Enter Comp Off Period Name in Search Box for Comp Off Tab

testSteps.description: 1: Enter Comp Off Period Name in Search Box for Comp Off Tab ({parentTab=Leave Management, childTab=View Request Status, compOffPeriod=25-Sep-2022, tab=Comp Off})

children.description: Given User is logged into MIS
When User is on MIS Home Page
When User clicks on "View Request Status" sub tab of "Leave Management" tab
When User clicks on "Comp Off" Tab
When User Enters "25-Sep-2022" period in search box for "Comp Off" tab
Then Verify "25-Sep-2022" Period is filtered for "Comp Off" tab
